  "body": "**Is your feature request related to a problem? Please describe.**\r\nAccording to eip4844 spec we can't broadcast full blob txs - https://eips.ethereum.org/EIPS/eip-4844#networking\r\n\r\n**Describe the solution you'd like**\r\nCheck if tx is blob-type and if is, only announce hash\r\n\r\n**Additional context**\r\nIt is blocked by 2 PRs:\r\nhttps://github.com/NethermindEth/nethermind/pull/4867 - we need TxType.Blob to be able to catch the difference with old-type txs\r\nhttps://github.com/NethermindEth/nethermind/pull/4866 - we will need a small refactor in eth68 `SendTransactions`\r\n\r\nIt requires changes made on top of PRs above.\r\nIt will be quick and small change, making issue to not forget about it",
